发现者小组-开发公约 v1.0

一. "七个禁止"
1. 禁止对非商业项目进行买卖,参与者将会被踢出小组和禁止使用项目
2. 禁止在作者非同意情况下,搬运内容,第一次则删除警告,第二次踢出小组
3. 禁止发表损害国家利益的言论和项目，违反者将删除，并承担法律责任
4. 禁止侮辱成员和使用者,同时使用者发现问题也不得侮辱,应当指出错误,以使得开发者进行修复
5. 禁止在项目PR恶意内容和恶意代码,对于pr代码,应当测试并检查后再发布
6. 禁止非法集资,以小组名义筹集资金等
7. 禁止对开发者小组下面的项目进行商业化操作

二. "四个鼓励"
1. 鼓励发表优秀项目和优秀想法
2. 鼓励打击损害版权利益的行为
3. 鼓励贡献和宣传正面形象
4. 鼓励将项目在论坛允许情况下,发表各大论坛

三."两个注意"
1. 注意以项目规定格式贡献内容
2. 注意项目是否支持下一步开发

                            Discoverer Group - Development Convention v1.0

I. "Seven Prohibitions"
1. It is forbidden to buy or sell non-commercial projects, participants will be kicked out of the group and prohibited from using the project.
2. It is forbidden to carry the contents without the author's consent. The first time the warning is deleted and the second time the team is kicked out.
3. It is forbidden to publish speeches and projects that harm the national interest. Violators will be deleted and will bear legal responsibility.
4. It is forbidden to insult members and users, and users should not be insulted when they find problems. They should point out errors so that developers can fix them.
5. Prohibit malicious content and malicious code in the project PR, for pr code, should be tested and checked before publishing
6. Prohibit illegal fundraising, raise funds in the name of the group, etc.
7. Prohibit commercialization of projects under the developer team

2. "Four encouragements"
1. Encourage the publication of excellent projects and excellent ideas
2. Encourage the fight against copyright infringement
3. Encourage contributions and promote positive images
4. Encourage the project to be published in the forums as permitted by the forum.

Three "two attentions"
1. Pay attention to contributing content in the format specified by the project
2. Note whether the project supports next development
